r relations contact us news center careers about us company profile pldt is the leading telecommunications and digital services provider in the philippines through its principal business groups – fixed line wireless and others – pldt offers a wide range of telecommunications and digital services across the philippines’ most extensive fiber optic backbone and fixed line and cellular networks pldt is listed on the philippine stock exchange psetel and its american depositary shares are listed on the new york stock exchange nysephi pldt has one of the largest market capitalizations among philippine­listed companies what drives pldt pldt is the largest and most diversified telecommunications company in the philippines notwithstanding the many technological changes that pldt will encounter in the future one thing will remain steadfast  its commitment to serving the nation and providing communications solutions to filipinos learn more pldts businesses pldt is the largest and most diversified telecommunications company in the philippines we have organized our business into three main segments learn more company leadership we at pldt are committed in bringing fiber optic technology which allows us to simultaneously deliver voice video and data services at much faster speed and larger capacity to residences and buildings  learn more company timeline when pldt was incorporated and given the franchise to establish and operate telephone services in the country on november   a typhoon had just ravaged eastern visayas bicol peninsula and samar learn more corporate governance pldt is committed to the highest standards of corporate governance as articulated in our articles of incorporation bylaws manual on corporate governance cg manual code of business conduct and ethics code of ethics and pertinent laws rules and regulations learn more corporate citizenship comrel is the face of pldt’s corporate social responsibility its longstanding interaction with grassroots communities from urban communities to the farflung rural areas across the country make known the thrust and services of pldt thereby realizing the convergence of business and social responsibility learn more contact us give us a call a text message or an email for your questions inquiries and suggestions learn more about pldt what drives pldt pldts businesses company leadership company timeline corporate governance corporate citizenship contact us investor relations disclosures annual reports sustainability report financial results presentations shareholder information news center news features archives careers why work for pldt job opportunities student programs pldt corporate office ramon cojuangco building makati ave corner ayala ave legaspi village makati city metro manila philippines  for customers  to  for directory assistance  for investors   for media      mediapldtcomph privacy policy  terms of use   pldt inc pldt subsidiaries  official pldt website pldt homepldt sme nationpldt alphapldt globalpldt subsidiaries search pldt home pldt sme nation pldt alpha pldt global pldt subsidiaries search pldt alpha is the trusted expert endtoend ict partner of the top enterprise market delivering innovative ict solutions and a premium grade customer experience go to pldt alpha website → pldt home believes that the strongest connections are at home by providing a compelling suite of multimedia services and solutions filipino families stay connected and can easily access quality entertainment at the comfort of their homes go to the pldt home website → pldt sme nation draws inspiration from the unique filipino entrepreneurial spirit formed to boost and empower the small and mediumsized businesses that form the essential backbone of the philippine economy go to pldt sme nation website → enjoy limitless possibilities with international services only from pldt global we are committed to be the leading offshore filipino ict company go to pldt global website → smart sun epldt smart communications 