es in the s isbn    a b history pldt retrieved    pldt drops long distance soon to be called pldt inc rappler april   retrieved june     business  lopezes to sell  of meralco to pldt  inquirernet businessinquirernet  retrieved     top stockholders as of december   pldt retrieved    pldt home ultera support library faq   globe  faq  volume boost   a b terms and conditions   tattoo free installation promofaqs   republic act no  the consumer act of the philippines  external linksedit official website smart communications v t e pldt chairman manuel v pangilinan president and ceo napoleon l nazareno mobility smart communications tnt sun cellular fixedline pldt landline digitel internet pldt home fibr telpad home dsl home bro smart bro sun broadband technology chikka smart money aces mabuhay satellite epldt outsourcing spi global  media tv nation gv  abi cignal pilipinas global network hastings holdings businessworld  the philippine star  philippine daily inquirer  unitel  utilities meralco  annual revenue php  billion fy   net income php  billion fy   employees   stock symbol pse tel v t e philippine telecommunications companies abscbn sky absc globe bayantel pldt digitel smart vega witribe v t e pse composite index companies of the philippines ayala aboitiz equity ventures alliance global ayala land aboitiz power bdo bloomberry resorts bpi dmci edc emperador first gen globe gt capital ictsi jollibee jg summit lt group metrobank megaworld meralco metro pacific petron pldt rfm corporation robinsons land semirara mining sm investments san miguel sm prime universal robina retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlepldtoldid categories pldttelecommunications companies of the philippinescompanies based in manilacompanies based in makatitechnology companies established in  establishments in the philippinescompanies listed on the philippine stock exchangecompanies listed on the new york stock exchangentt communicationsntt docomohidden categories articles needing additional